{
  "stem": "3165.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They said, oh, don't have to worry now.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] The Germans not coming back.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The war will be finished, hopefully soon.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So here now one day, I'm in the field with the cattle and this other girl, friend of mine from next neighbor right there.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And just then I said to myself, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I think I'm-- I'm going to leave now.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I asked-- and I ask the girl, I tell her, I says, would you mind taking my cattle back home and tell the people that I'll be back later, later at night, whatever.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "What was the name of the family that you were staying with?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Ah, I wish I could remember.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't think I even knew their last names.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I always call her [NON-ENGLISH], which means like madam, you know, and [NON-ENGLISH], like sir, you know?",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't think I even called them by their names or-- last name for sure I didn't know.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So right that day I thought, I'm going to run to the city, which is Miedzyrzecz, next to this little-- to this village.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I asked the girl would she mind, you know, looking after the cows and take them home and make sure you tell the people that I went into-- I think I could have told them that I was going to the city, and I'll be back, you know, late at night.",
      "word_count": 52
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she said, sure, I'll do that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I walked away, and I walked to the city.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I came to the city, and sure enough, there was some Jewish people already.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That came from hiding.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were coming out of hiding.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "From hiding.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there was one family, I stayed with them, not for very long.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
